name: 植物园
desc: Level effect: stealth cancels the cooldown; Shaymin is permanently forbidden to heal; the healing rate of other Pokémon is greatly increased. \nVictory condition: defeat Shaymin
desc_tw: 關卡效果：潛行取消冷卻時間；謝米永久禁療；其他精靈治療率大幅提升。\n勝利條件：擊敗謝米
desc_en: Level effect: stealth cancels the cooldown; Shaymin is permanently forbidden to heal; the healing rate of other Pokémon is greatly increased. \nVictory condition: defeat Shaymin
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과: 잠행 쿨타임 취소하며 쉐이미 영구 치료 금지, 기타 포켓몬의 치료율이 대폭 상승.  \n승리 조건: 쉐이미 격파하기
reviewPlot: After passing the test, you got a green slate with #L10##C0x57D700#Jumpluff pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_tw: 通過考驗後，你們獲得了一塊畫有#L10##C0x57D700#毽子棉圖案#C0x5B545B##L0#的綠色石板。
reviewPlot_en: After passing the test, you got a green slate with #L10##C0x57D700#Jumpluff pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_kr: 시련을 통과 후 당신들은 #L10##C0x57D700#솜솜코 도안#C0x5B545B##L0#이 그려진 초록색 석판을 얻었다.

name: 冰雪屋
desc: Level effect: The frozen target becomes unselectable, and you will fail if all of your allies are frozen; enemy will increase the control rate every round. \nVictory condition: win the battle
desc_tw: 關卡效果：冰凍目標變為不可選中，己方全體被冰凍則失敗；敵方每回合提升控制率。\n勝利條件：獲得戰鬥勝利
desc_en: Level effect: The frozen target becomes unselectable, and you will fail if all of your allies are frozen; enemy will increase the control rate every round. \nVictory condition: win the battle
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과: 얼음 목표가 선택 불가로 변경하고 아군 전체가 얼음되면 실패하며, 적들은 턴마다 제어율을 높인다. \n승리 조건: 전투 승리
reviewPlot: After passing the test, you got a blue slate painted with #L10##C0x00CED7#Staryu pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_tw: 通過考驗後，你們獲得了一塊畫著#L10##C0x00CED7#海星星圖案#C0x5B545B##L0#的藍色石板。
reviewPlot_en: After passing the test, you got a blue slate painted with #L10##C0x00CED7#Staryu pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_kr: 시련을 통과 후 당신들은 #L10##C0x00CED7#별가사리 도안#C0x5B545B##L0#이 그려진 파란색 석판을 얻었다.

name: 镜之城
desc: Level effect: Enemy will become a mirror image, and the enemy will be healed when attacked by the mirror target. \nVictory condition: win the battle
desc_tw: 關卡效果：對位的敵人會成為鏡像，敵方受到鏡像目標攻擊會獲得治療。\n勝利條件：獲得戰鬥勝利
desc_en: Level effect: Enemy will become a mirror image, and the enemy will be healed when attacked by the mirror target. \nVictory condition: win the battle
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과: 대응하는 위치의 적은 거울이 되며, 적에게 거울 대상 공격을 당하면 치료를 받는다.  \n승리 조건: 전투 승리
reviewPlot: After passing the test, you got a white slate painted with #L10##C0xAEAEA8# Caterpie pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_tw: 通過考驗後，你們獲得了一塊畫著#L10##C0xAEAEA8#綠毛蟲圖案#C0x5B545B##L0#的白色石板。
reviewPlot_en: After passing the test, you got a white slate painted with #L10##C0xAEAEA8# Caterpie pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_kr: 시련을 통과 후 당신들은 #L10##C0xAEAEA8#캐터피 도안#C0x5B545B##L0#이 그려진 하얀색 석판을 얻었다.

name: 火炎岛
desc: Level effect: Each Charizard have different abilities, try to survive! \nVictory condition: still alive at the beginning of round 7
desc_tw: 關卡效果：噴火龍各自擁有不同的能力，努力活下去！\n勝利條件：第7回合開始時仍然存活
desc_en: Level effect: Each Charizard have different abilities, try to survive! \nVictory condition: still alive at the beginning of round 7
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과 : 리자몽은 각자 다른 능력을 가지고 열심히 살아간다! \n승리 조건: 7라운드 시작 시 여전히 살아남기
reviewPlot: After passing the test, you got a red slate painted with #L10##C0xEE2417#Oddish pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_tw: 通過考驗後，你們獲得了一塊畫著#L10##C0xEE2417#走路草圖案#C0x5B545B##L0#的紅色石板。
reviewPlot_en: After passing the test, you got a red slate painted with #L10##C0xEE2417#Oddish pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_kr: 시련을 통과 후 당신들은 #L10##C0xEE2417#뚜벅초 도안#C0x5B545B##L0#이 그려진 빨간색 석판을 얻었다.

name: 幻境
desc: Level effect: Alakazam hides himself among the illusions, find him! When Alakazam is in danger, he will shift himself with another illusion.\nVictory condition: defeat the true Alakazam
desc_tw: 關卡效果：胡地的真實意念隱藏在多個分身之中，找到他！胡地在遇到危險時會轉移自己的真實意念哦\n勝利條件：擊敗胡地的真實意念
desc_en: Level effect: Alakazam hides himself among the illusions, find him! When Alakazam is in danger, he will shift himself with another illusion.\nVictory condition: defeat the true Alakazam
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과 : 후딘의 진의는 여러 개의 분신 속에 숨어 있어, 그를 찾아라! 후딘은 위험에 처했을 때 자신의 진의를 옮긴다. \n승리 조건 : 후딘의 진의를 격파하기
reviewPlot: After passing the test, you got a purple slate painted with #L10##C0xC817EE# Machamp pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_tw: 通過考驗後，你們獲得了一塊畫著#L10##C0xC817EE#怪力圖案#C0x5B545B##L0#的紫色石板。
reviewPlot_en: After passing the test, you got a purple slate painted with #L10##C0xC817EE# Machamp pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_kr: 시련을 통과 후 당신들은 #L10##C0xC817EE#괴력몬 도안#C0x5B545B##L0#이 그려진 보라색 석판을 얻었다.

name: 摩天轮
desc: Level effect: The naughty Hoopa loves to lie, find out the Hoopa who tells the truth can get clues. \nVictory condition: defeat all Hoopa who tells the truth
desc_tw: 關卡效果：調皮的胡帕愛說謊，找到說真話的胡帕才能得到線索。\n勝利條件：擊敗所有說真話的胡帕
desc_en: Level effect: The naughty Hoopa loves to lie, find out the Hoopa who tells the truth can get clues. \nVictory condition: defeat all Hoopa who tells the truth
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과: 장난꾸러기 후파는 거짓말을 잘 하고, 진실을 말하는 후파를 찾아야 단서를 얻을 수 있다. \n승리 조건: 진실을 말하는 후파를 모두 격파하기
reviewPlot: After passing the test, you got a yellow slate painted with #L10##C0xEEE017#Goldeen pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_tw: 通過考驗後，你們獲得了一塊畫著#L10##C0xEEE017#角金魚圖案#C0x5B545B##L0#的黃色石板。
reviewPlot_en: After passing the test, you got a yellow slate painted with #L10##C0xEEE017#Goldeen pattern #C0x5B545B##L0#.
reviewPlot_kr: 시련을 통과 후 당신들은 #L10##C0xEEE017#콘치 도안#C0x5B545B##L0#이 그려진 노란색 석판을 얻었다.

name: 救援
desc: Level effect: protect the injured Feebas. \nVictory condition: win the game and Feebas survive
desc_tw: 關卡效果：保護好受傷的醜醜魚。\n勝利條件：獲得遊戲勝利且醜醜魚存活
desc_en: Level effect: protect the injured Feebas. \nVictory condition: win the game and Feebas survive
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과: 다친 빈티나를 잘 보호하라. \n승리 조건: 게임 승리, 또한 빈티나 살아남기
reviewPlot: After driving away the teen hooligans, you rescued the injured Feebas and temporarily subdued it in the Pokéball.
reviewPlot_tw: 趕跑不良少年後，你們救下了受傷的醜醜魚，並將它暫時收服在精靈球中。
reviewPlot_en: After driving away the teen hooligans, you rescued the injured Feebas and temporarily subdued it in the Pokéball.
reviewPlot_kr: 불량 소년을 쫓아낸 뒤 다친 빈티나를 구해 몬스터볼에 잠시 넣어 둔다.

name: 藏宝地
desc: Level effect: The colorful pillars seem to be related to the previously obtained slate. What does the pattern on the slate represent? \nVictory condition: win the game
desc_tw: 關卡效果：五顏六色的柱子，似乎和之前獲得的石板有某種關聯，石板上的圖案又是代表什麼呢？\n勝利條件：獲得遊戲勝利
desc_en: Level effect: The colorful pillars seem to be related to the previously obtained slate. What does the pattern on the slate represent? \nVictory condition: win the game
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과 : 알록달록한 기둥은 기존에 얻었던 석판과 어떤 연관이 있는 것 같은데, 석판에 도안은 무엇을 의미하는 걸까? \n승리 조건: 게임 승리
reviewPlot: After solving the mystery in the desert, you found a beautiful statue of Milotic.
reviewPlot_tw: 破解了荒漠中的謎題後，你們找到了一尊精美的美納斯雕像。
reviewPlot_en: After solving the mystery in the desert, you found a beautiful statue of Milotic.
reviewPlot_kr: 황량한 사막의 수수께끼를 푼 후에 당신들은 정교하고 아름다운 밀로틱 조각상을 발견했다.

name: 抢夺
desc: Level effect: Be careful, don't break the statue of Milotic. \nVictory condition: win the game within one round and the statue of Milotic is not broken
desc_tw: 關卡效果：小心點，可別把美納斯雕像打碎了。\n勝利條件：在一回合內獲得遊戲勝利且美納斯雕像未破碎
desc_en: Level effect: Be careful, don't break the statue of Milotic. \nVictory condition: win the game within one round and the statue of Milotic is not broken
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과: 조심해, 밀로틱 조각상을 깨뜨리지마라. \n승리 조건: 1라운드 내 게임 승리, 또한 밀로틱 조각상 깨지지 않기
reviewPlot: The statue o fMilotic was snatched by the Team Rockets. In the process of retaking the statue of Milotic, you accidentally fell out of the airship...
reviewPlot_tw: 美納斯雕像被火箭隊一行搶走，在奪回美納斯雕像的過程中，你不慎跌下飛艇……
reviewPlot_en: The statue o fMilotic was snatched by the Team Rockets. In the process of retaking the statue of Milotic, you accidentally fell out of the airship...
reviewPlot_kr: 밀로틱 조각상을 로켓단에게 빼앗기고, 탈환하다가 당신은 비행선에서 떨어졌다…

name: 神殿
desc: Level effect: Fight the Team Rockets with Milotic! \nVictory condition: win the game
desc_tw: 關卡效果：和美納斯一起打跑火箭隊吧！\n勝利條件：獲得遊戲勝利
desc_en: Level effect: Fight the Team Rockets with Milotic! \nVictory condition: win the game
desc_kr: 스테이지 효과 : 밀로틱과 함께 로켓단을 쫓아 버리자! \n승리 조건: 게임 승리
reviewPlot: With the help of Milotic, you defeated the Team Rockets and won the final victory of the Summer Adventure Explore event!
reviewPlot_tw: 在美納斯的幫助下，你們擊敗了火箭隊，並獲得了夏日祭探險活動的最終勝利！
reviewPlot_en: With the help of Milotic, you defeated the Team Rockets and won the final victory of the Summer Adventure Explore event!
reviewPlot_kr: 밀로틱의 도움으로 로켓단을 물리치고 여름축제 탐험의 최종 승리를 얻었다!
